{"tid":1012823,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解就唔肯承認自己係貪錢 為錢？","createTime":"2019-02-08T01:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T13:42:15.000Z","uid":224885,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8e499aac73185b9b23ef5dca88be7cd5abf5005e","tid":1012823,"uid":224885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T01:22:21.000Z","msg":"港女進化騙術層出不窮<br />\n口口聲聲話唔係為錢 唔係錢問題<br />\n但係港女身邊不論大大小小事都要幫佢出錢<br />\n唔出錢就嬲 放係心入面<br />\n而用心為佢做既事就唔當係咩<br />\n你為佢付出二十萬 佢可能只係為係付出過一萬都無<br />\n佢既錢就洗哂落自己度 無錢就搵你拎<br />\n從頭到尾只係為左自己 <br />\n仲要咩都唔會做 唔識做 淨係攤開隻手 唔為佢做又嬲<br />\n之後就搵藉口 性格唔岩 又話唔愛 <br />\n一句錢既觀念唔同 屈哂機<br />\n私底下做既野 收兵又唔肯比人知<br />\n拍拖唔既事又唔比人知<br />\n推哂問題落你度 你唔好 分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ad19f37bf8189db913aefa325376bda995c773","tid":1012823,"uid":224107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T01:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sad but true"},{"pid":"a11299d8e01ef3c1e7eb98de035f4be2a885c8a9","tid":1012823,"uid":203543,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T01:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvR5OYS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvR5OYS.png&h=720ec687&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0b6cb0f14f5a438615eb0d12433d3ecf9872225","tid":1012823,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:31:55.000Z","msg":"畀女飛嬲嬲數臭港女？"},{"pid":"0db2fbae8c2b096cd8e7f69bb8f64c14493db238","tid":1012823,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚肉酸"},{"pid":"c17c413c1621f9cfd049bc49e4b786ef1c6f01ee","tid":1012823,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T12:37:03.000Z